#  Telecom Customer Churn Analysis

An end-to-end data analytics project that explores customer churn in a telecom company using **Python**, **PostgreSQL**, and **Power BI**. The project focuses on identifying churn patterns, analyzing revenue impact, and building an interactive dashboard to support business decisions.

---

##  Tech Stack

* Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn)
* PostgreSQL
* Power BI
* DAX
* Git & GitHub

---

##  Workflow

```
Raw Dataset
    ↓
Data Cleaning (Python)
    ↓
Exploratory Data Analysis
    ↓
PostgreSQL Analysis
    ↓
Power BI Dashboard
    ↓
Business Insights
```

