##  Key Insights

* Customer churn rate: **26.54%**
* Month-to-Month contracts have the highest churn.
* Fiber Optic customers are more likely to churn.
* New customers (low tenure) churn the most.
* Competitor-related reasons account for most customer losses.
* Revenue at risk exceeds **$3.6M**.

